            <div class="space-y-4">
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">Two years ago, a SaaS startup hired me for their marketing site. They needed something impressive‚Äîinvestors were visiting, funding round depended on it. I made the mistake of skipping planning.</p>

              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed"><strong>The wrong route: Durable alone</strong></p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">Generated a complete site in 30 seconds. Looked okay. Published. Then the problems started.</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">Week 1: Missing pages‚Äîno pricing comparison, no security page, no integrations overview.</p>
