              <div class="bg-orange-100 border-l-[4px] border-orange-500 p-4 my-4">
                <p class="text-sm text-orange-900 font-medium"><strong>The Durable win:</strong> Generated complete bakery site in 28 seconds. Published same day. Got 5 catering orders first month. Owner's thrilled. No planning needed for something that simple.</p>
              </div>

              <div class="bg-amber-100 border-l-[4px] border-amber-500 p-4 my-4">
                <p class="text-sm text-amber-900 font-medium"><strong>The brutal truth:</strong> Durable for simple sites where speed matters more than perfection. Relume for anything complex, anything investor-facing, anything that NEEDS to work. If you're building something that matters, plan first. If you're building something simple, just ship it.</p>
              </div>

              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">I've learned this lesson the expensive way. Skip planning with Relume, pay the price later. Use Durable for complex projects, hit limitations immediately. The right tool for the right job‚Äîevery single time.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-50 to-teal-50 border-[3px] border-gray-200 p-8 my-8">
          <p class="text-gray-900 font-black text-lg mb-4">The Best Workflow: Relume ‚Üí Framer</p>
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-teal-600 text-white flex items-center justify-center font-black flex-shrink-0">1</div>
              <div>
